      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Heat a large, wide-based pan (preferably non-stick with a matching lid) with a drizzle of <strong>vegetable oil </strong>over a medium-high heat</p><p>Once hot, add your <strong>chicken gyozas </strong>and cook for 5 min</p><p>When the gyozas have had 5 min, remove from the gyozas from the heat and carefully add a splash of <strong>cold water</strong>, then return to the heat and cook, covered, for a further 5 min</p><p>Tip: Be careful when adding the water to the pan, it may splash!</p>",
