    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once the onion is caramelised, add your <strong>curry powder</strong>, <strong>ginger & garlic paste</strong>, <strong>chilli flakes </strong>(can't handle the heat? Go easy!) and 1 tbsp<span class=\"text-purple\"> [1 1/2 tbsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tbsp] </span><strong>flour</strong></p><p>Cook for 1 min or until fragrant</p>",
