    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Once fragrant, add your <strong>soy sauce</strong>, <strong>chicken stock mix </strong>and 200ml <span class=\"text-purple\">[260ml] </span><span class=\"text-danger\">[340ml]</span> <strong>boiled water</strong></p><p>Add the <strong>drained noodles </strong>and cook for 2 min or until fully coated – this is your<strong> Japanese-style curry udon</strong></p>",
