      "instruction": "<p>Serve the <strong>Japanese-style curry udon </strong>topped with the <strong>chicken gyozas </strong>and<strong> quick-pickled carrot</strong></p><p>Garnish with the <strong>sliced spring onion</strong></p><p>Enjoy!</p>",
